Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.12,0:27:57.40,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}風の軌跡　辿って
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.67,0:28:10.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}過ぎ去る日々の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.96,0:28:14.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}いつのまに閉じ込めた
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.19,0:28:17.31,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}もう一人のわたしが
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.39,0:28:20.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}呼ぶ声のするほうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.56,0:28:23.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}投げかけられた視線
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.80,0:28:26.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}気づかないふりをして
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.03,0:28:32.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}素直になれるための理由探してたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.86,0:28:37.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}悔しくて泣きたくなる時は
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.30,0:28:39.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}立ち止まって
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.32,0:28:42.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}靴紐　固く結んで
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.54,0:28:47.64,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}ゆっくりとスピードを上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.28,0:28:53.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}風の軌跡辿って　加速していくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.80,0:28:55.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Keep On Runnin'！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.59,0:28:56.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.94,0:29:00.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真っ直ぐに  Way To Go
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.35,0:29:06.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}乾いた大地蹴って　駆け抜けていくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.82,0:29:08.54,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Don't Stop Feelin'！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.66,0:29:13.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}確かめたい　君とふたりで
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.78,0:29:17.38,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}何処まででも　まっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.40,0:29:21.45,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,300)}Keep On Runnin'！
