Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.12,0:27:57.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}追寻风的轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.67,0:28:10.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}在逝去的时光中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.96,0:28:14.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}曾几何时封闭了心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.19,0:28:17.31,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}另一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.39,0:28:20.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}向着呼唤声的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.56,0:28:23.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}投向我的视线的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.80,0:28:26.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都装作没有察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.03,0:28:32.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}寻找着能够变得坦率的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.86,0:28:37.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}后悔的时候想要哭泣的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.30,0:28:39.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}总是停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.32,0:28:42.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}系紧鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.54,0:28:47.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}慢慢提升速度
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.28,0:28:53.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}追寻风的轨迹 渐渐加速了哦
Comment: 0,0:28:53.80,0:28:55.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Keep On Runnin'！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.59,0:28:56.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}已经停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.94,0:29:00.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}向着正前方 Way To Go
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.35,0:29:06.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}踢开干涸的大地 这就赶来
Comment: 0,0:29:06.82,0:29:08.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Don't Stop Feelin'！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.66,0:29:13.51,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}想要确认 和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.78,0:29:17.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}无论何处 向着正前方
Comment: 0,0:29:17.40,0:29:21.45,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,300)}Keep On Runnin'！
